settings.description: luigi needs to stop, this is getting tiring
Luigi must take the hammer bro suit on his airship and take it to bowser.
a whole castle filled with bricks that can be turned into koopas and mushrooms? what a dream! course, Bowser's waiting at the end to ruin the fun!
i think i made this feel a lot like a standard level
The 'Ultimate" airship is hare! You must board it and get through it, then fight Boom Boom, the airship creator! Don't die or you will be forced to restart, he is a lot harder this time!

This level has 5 ace coins, so you need to recollect it,
Infact, this is my nice level ever made, you need a hammer to destroy it by getting the 3-ups in a giant question mark block.
No low budget flagpole this time!
Ice, munchers, flurries, penguins, and... shoes?! seems like this wild combo is something that's a bit toooo chill to exist, but it does!
